wt.util.xml.xpath

Class NodeListCallback

  • java.lang.Object
    • AbstractXPathCallback
      • wt.util.xml.xpath.NodeListCallback

  • public class NodeListCallback
extends AbstractXPathCallback
    This class may be used as a simple callback to obtain a NodeList from a particular xpath. Any attempt to process any other type will result in a DOMException.NOT_SUPPORTED_ERR being thrown back to the calling body.

    Supported API: true

    Extendable: true
